---

## ğŸ“Œ Notes

* Passwords are hashed using bcrypt before storing
* JWT tokens expire after a defined time (optional)
* Only the owner of a TODO can edit/delete it
* You can extend this app with:

  * Pagination
  * Filtering (by status)
  * Refresh tokens

